productBaseInfoV1.title: Apple iPhone 6 Plus
productBaseInfoV1.productDescription: The iPhone 6 Plus is not only bigger, it's better in every way. The iPhone 6 Plus boasts a large Retina Display on a slim, smooth metal surface. It is the perfect combination of hardware and software functions and it can be in your pocket right now. Sleek Design The best part of the iPhone 6 Plus is its innovative design. The cover glass curves around the sides to join the anodized aluminum enclosure in a modest design with no distinct edges or gaps. It's a seamless fusion of metal and glass that feels incredible in your hands. Bigger and Better Display The iPhone 6 Plus comes with a 5.5-inch Retina HD display that can produce a pixel resolution of 1920x1080 at 401 Pixels per inch. The Multi-touch Display comes with full sRGB color standards, white balance and brightness. The phone also uses UV light to rightly position the display's liquid crystals, resulting in a better viewing experience. State-of-the-Art Technology The iPhone 6 Plus comes with Apple's latest microchip - the all-new A8 Chip. This microchip's graphics and CPU performance are faster than iPhone 5's A7 chip while managing a larger display and other features. It uses an advanced 20-nanometer process that results in incredibly quick performances. M8 Coprocessor Technology and Sensors This phone comes with an M8 coprocessor that measures data from its sensors such as the accelerometer, compass, and gyroscope, allowing you to measure your steps and distance. It even measures changes in elevation. Stunning Photography The iPhone 6 Plus comes with an iSight camera that makes it easier to take pictures. With large 1.5-micron pixels and f/2.2 aperture, it is arguably the most popular camera that captures 1080p HD videos at 60 frames per second. You can also take slow motion videos in 720p resolution at 240 frames per second. Faster Connectivity The iPhone 6 comes with an ultra-fast wireless technology that allows you to connect to high-speed wireless networks wherever you go. With 802.11ac WiFi, you can connect to wireless networks up to 3 times faster than 802.11n networks. It also has Bluetooth 4.0. Touch ID Enjoy security at your fingertips thanks to the iPhone 6 Plus' fingerprint password that allows you to protect your phone from other users. It not only unlocks your phone, it can also be used to approve purchases on the App Store or iTunes. iOS 8 The iPhone 6 Plus comes with the latest operating system from Apple - iOS 8. This operating system comes with a number of incredible features that streamline your workflow wherever you go. The iPhone 6 Plus also comes with a bunch of new apps that make everyday lively, exciting and organized.
